</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="card">
      
      <h1>Privacy Policy – DoseHarbor</h1>
      <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> [Insert Date]</p>

      <p>
        DoseHarbor ("we", "our", or "us") respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal information.
        This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use our mobile application.
      </p>

      <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>

      <h3>Personal Information</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Name (optional)</li>
        <li>Email address (if you create an account)</li>
        <li>Profile details (age, weight, etc. if entered)</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Health & Medication Data</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Medication names</li>
        <li>Dosage schedules</li>
        <li>Reminder preferences</li>
        <li>Medication history</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="highlight">This data is sensitive and handled with strict security measures.</p>

      <h3>Device & Usage Data</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Device type and OS version</li>
        <li>App usage and interactions</li>
        <li>Crash logs and diagnostics</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Provide medication reminders and tracking</li>
        <li>Improve app performance and features</li>
        <li>Personalize user experience</li>
        <li>Ensure security and prevent misuse</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="highlight">We do NOT sell your data.</p>

      <h2>3. Data Storage & Security</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Data may be stored locally and/or securely in the cloud</li>
        <li>Industry-standard encryption is used</li>
        <li>Access is restricted and protected</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Data Sharing</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>With your consent (e.g., sharing with family or doctor)</li>
        <li>With trusted service providers (hosting, analytics)</li>
        <li>When required by law</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="highlight">We never share data for advertising.</p>

      <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Access your data</li>
        <li>Update or correct your data</li>
        <li>Request deletion</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Contact us at: <strong>[your-email@example.com]</strong></p>

      <h2>6. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        DoseHarbor is not intended for children under 13.
        We do not knowingly collect personal data from children.
      </p>

      <h2>7. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>
        We retain data only as long as necessary to provide services or comply with legal obligations.
      </p>

      <h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Significant changes will be communicated to users.
      </p>

      <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        Email: <strong>[your-email@example.com]</strong><br/>
        App Name: DoseHarbor
      </p>

      <div class="footer">
        © 2026 DoseHarbor. All rights reserved.
      </div>

